Package: valkey-server
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends:
 ${misc:Pre-Depends},
Depends:
 adduser,
 valkey-tools (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
Recommends: logrotate
Description: Persistent key-value database with network interface (server)
 Valkey is an advanced key-value store. It is often referred to as a data
 structure server since keys can contain strings, hashes, lists, sets and
 sorted sets.
 .
 This package contains the Valkey server.

Package: valkey-sentinel
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends:
 ${misc:Pre-Depends},
Depends:
 adduser,
 valkey-tools (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Persistent key-value database with network interface (sentinel)
 Valkey Sentinel provides high availability for Valkey. It monitors Valkey
 instances and automatically performs failover.
 .
 This package contains the Valkey Sentinel daemon.

Package: valkey-tools
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Suggests:
 ruby-redis,
Description: Persistent key-value database with network interface (client tools)
 Valkey is an advanced key-value store. It is often referred to as a data
 structure server since keys can contain strings, hashes, lists, sets and
 sorted sets.
 .
 This package contains supporting administrative tools: valkey-cli,
 valkey-benchmark, valkey-check-aof, and valkey-check-rdb.
